    "Instagram carousel slide, clean modern layout, white background,\nprofessional furniture ecommerce aesthetic.\n\nTOP TEXT (bold, dark charcoal, 28px, centered):\n\"Está cansado de pagar caro por fotos para seu ecommerce de móveis?\"\nSUBTEXT below it (medium weight, 22px, centered):\n\"Se liga na solução! Essa imagem aqui foi feita 100% com IA!\"\n\nCENTER IMAGE: ultra-realistic AI-generated product photo of a \npremium walnut wood armchair with cream bouclé fabric seat, \npure white seamless background, three-point studio lighting, \nsoft drop shadow underneath, sharp wood grain and fabric texture \ndetails, front angle with slight 15-degree rotation, commercial \necommerce catalog quality, photorealistic, 8K, Publicado en la plataforma de Amazon.，no watermark\n\nBOTTOM TEXT (bold, with right arrow emoji →, centered, 22px):\n\"Passe para ver mais →\"\n\nOverall slide style: minimal, luxurious, high-end Brazilian \nfurniture marketplace aesthetic, no clutter, lots of white space",
